description:
A flexible glass shower door seal at a fraction of the cost of our competitors!  
 
35" Shower Door Seal attaches to the bottom of your glass panel to prevent water from leaking out of your shower.
 
This clear plastic door seal has a rigid formed u-channel that simply slips onto the bottom edge of your glass door, making installation a breeze! No glue or tools needed! 
 
Dimensions:
 
- 35" wide
- 3/4" thick seal with a 1/2" u-channel
 
This seal is in stock and ready to ship out to your home from our warehouse, located in beautiful Denver, Colorado. Shower seals are shipped usually within 3 business days of your order. 
 
Works great with our Prosto brand Frameless Showers, you can find them listed on our ebay store.

This clear plastic seal has a rigid formed u-channel that simply slips onto the side edge of your glass panel, making installation a breeze! No glue or tools needed!

Perfect for use with our frameless showers - to view these items visit our store on ebay.
